posting_body: ['7413 142nd Avenue East, Sumner, WA 98390', 'The Retreat Apartments are located in Sumner, Washington, known to many as the Rhubarb Pie Capital of the World."', 'Despite all of its industrial growth, Sumner has maintained its small-town, friendly feel.', 'With close access to major highways, Downtown Sumner, a variety of shopping options, walking, and biking trails, parks, and schools; the location is ideal and the property is stunning.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Fireplace', 'Washer & Dryer', 'In Every Unit', 'Garbage Disposal', 'Carpet/Vinyl Flooring', 'Updated Appliances', 'Dining Room', 'Community Features:', 'Picnic Area', 'Management & Maintenance On-Site', 'Translation Service Available', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Semi-Private Entry', 'Waterscape', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
